<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4597078>
    dc:description "FIG. 2. — Photograph of Ruthenosaurus russellorum n. gen., n. sp. holotype (MNHN.F.MCL-1) in dorsal view with preserved remains placed in articulation. Scale bar: 10 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4597078/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4597082>
    dc:description "FIG. 3. — Anterior dorsal vertebrae of Ruthenosaurus russellorum n. gen., n. sp. (MNHN.F.MCL-1): A, posterior view; B, dorsal view; C, left lateral view (anterior to the left). Scale bar: 3 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4597082/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4597084>
    dc:description "FIG. 4. — “Lumbars” (3), first caudal vertebra and sacral region of the axial skeleton of Ruthenosaurus russellorum n. gen., n. sp. (MNHN.F.MCL-1) in dorsal view. Scale bar: 5 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4597084/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4597086>
    dc:description "FIG. 5. — Right (A, B) and left (C, D) humeri of Ruthenosaurus russellorum n. gen., n. sp. (MNHN.F.MCL-1): A, ventral view; B, anterior view; C, dorsal view; D, ventral view. Note the low accessory ridge (a.r.) on the ventral surface of the proximal head and the deep entepicondylar groove (asterisk). Scale bar: 5 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4597086/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4597091>
    dc:description "FIG. 6. — Left ulna of Ruthenosaurus russellorum n. gen., n. sp. (MNHN.F.MCL-1): A, anterior view; B, medial view. Scale bar: 5 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4597091/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4597093>
    dc:description "FIG. 7. — Right ilium of Ruthenosaurus russellorum n. gen., n. sp. (MNHN.F.MCL-1): A, lateral view; B, medial view. Note the autapomorphic posterior process (p.p.) of the iliac blade. Scale bar: 5 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4597093/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4597095>
    dc:description "FIG. 8. — Right femur of Ruthenosaurus russellorum n. gen., n. sp. (MNHN.F.MCL-1):A, posterior view; B, dorsal view;C, anteroventral view; D, ventral view. Scale bar: 5 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4597095/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4597097>
    dc:description "FIG. 9. — Right tibia of Ruthenosaurus russellorum n. gen., n. sp. (MNHN.F.MCL-1): A, lateral view; B, posteromedial view; C, medial view. Scale bar: 5 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4597097/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

